metadata.description: A VSCode extension that promotes healthy coding habits by reminding you to take stretch breaks at regular intervals with automatic stretch videos.

metadata.scriptContent: pnpm run check-types && pnpm run lint && tsx esbuild.ts
pnpm run check-types && pnpm run lint && tsx esbuild.ts --production
pnpm run compile-tests && pnpm run compile && pnpm run lint
pnpm run package && pnpm run publish:vsce && pnpm run publish:ovsx
